        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: LIteral: \"Whereas immunogold-silver staining forGAD65 was more widespread and occurred primarily interminals and vesicle-containing dendrites. ...Terminals immunostained for IGRs and GAD65 madealmost exclusively symmetric synapses onto neuronal cellbodies, dendrites, or central terminals of primary affer-ents. \". Experimental description: - \"Male Sprague-Dawley rats (250 -350 g; Charles River,Raleigh, NC) were used for this study. \"" ;
